## Key Statistics

| Metric | Before | After |
|--------|--------|-------|
| **CSS Files** | 1 massive file | 15 organized modules |
| **JS Files** | 1 massive file | 17 organized modules |
| **Total Files** | 3 | 37 (34 code + 3 docs) |
| **Largest CSS** | 2,688 lines | 460 lines (mobile.css) |
| **Largest JS** | 4,257 lines | 1,057 lines (dom.js) |
| **Avg CSS Size** | 50KB | 3.9KB per file |
| **Avg JS Size** | 157KB | 9.5KB per file |

## Immediate Benefits

### âœ… Development
- **Find code 10x faster** - Jump directly to the module you need
- **Understand code easier** - Each file has a single, clear purpose
- **Debug faster** - Stack traces point to specific modules
- **Make changes safely** - Isolated modules reduce side effects

### âœ… Collaboration
- **No more merge conflicts** - Work on different modules simultaneously
- **Clearer code reviews** - Review only changed modules
- **Easier onboarding** - New developers understand structure quickly
- **Better ownership** - Clear responsibility for each module

### âœ… Performance
- **Better caching** - Browser caches each module separately
- **Faster updates** - Only redownload changed files
- **Parallel loading** - Browser can load multiple files at once
- **Smaller downloads** - On subsequent visits, cache hits are common

